    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo-fluidæ­å»ºä¸ªäººåšå®¢"><a href="#hexo-fluidæ­å»ºä¸ªäººåšå®¢" class="headerlink" title="hexo+fluidæ­å»ºä¸ªäººåšå®¢"></a>hexo+fluidæ­å»ºä¸ªäººåšå®¢</h1><h2 id="1-hexoå®‰è£…"><a href="#1-hexoå®‰è£…" class="headerlink" title="1 hexoå®‰è£…"></a>1 hexoå®‰è£…</h2><p>æœ¬åœ°åˆ›å»ºä¸€ä¸ªç›®å½•ï¼Œä¾‹å¦‚<code>hexo</code>ï¼Œç„¶åè¿›å…¥è¯¥ç›®å½•ï¼Œé€šè¿‡npmå®‰è£…ï¼š</p><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm">npm install -g hexo-<span class="hljs-keyword">cli</span><br>hexo -v<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-åˆ›å»ºhexoé¡¹ç›®"><a href="#2-åˆ›å»ºhexoé¡¹ç›®" class="headerlink" title="2 åˆ›å»ºhexoé¡¹ç›®"></a>2 åˆ›å»ºhexoé¡¹ç›®</h2><figure class="highlight mipsasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs mipsasm">hexo init <span class="hljs-keyword">blog</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword"></span>cd <span class="hljs-keyword">blog</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword"></span>npm <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-æœ¬åœ°å¯åŠ¨"><a href="#3-æœ¬åœ°å¯åŠ¨" class="headerlink" title="3 æœ¬åœ°å¯åŠ¨"></a>3 æœ¬åœ°å¯åŠ¨</h2><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo g</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo s</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>é€šè¿‡ <a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000</a> è®¿é—®é¡µé¢ï¼Œæ­¤æ—¶æ˜¯é»˜è®¤ä¸»é¢˜ï¼šlandscape</p><h2 id="4-æ›´æ¢ä¸»é¢˜"><a href="#4-æ›´æ¢ä¸»é¢˜" class="headerlink" title="4 æ›´æ¢ä¸»é¢˜"></a>4 æ›´æ¢ä¸»é¢˜</h2><p>hexoå®˜ç½‘ä¸»é¢˜ï¼š<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">Themes | Hexo</a></p><p>æ¨èä¸¤ä¸ªä¸»é¢˜ï¼Œä¸€ä¸ªæ˜¯<a href="https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-theme-next">NEXT</a>ï¼Œ å¦ä¸€ä¸ªæ˜¯<a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">fluid</a>ã€‚è¿™é‡Œæ›´æ¢ä¸»é¢˜ä¸º fluid ã€‚</p><p>æ¨èä»githubä¸‹è½½æœ€æ–°å‹ç¼©åŒ…ï¼š<a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid/releases">Releases Â· fluid-dev&#x2F;hexo-theme-fluid (github.com)</a>ï¼Œè§£å‹åˆ° <code>themes</code> ç›®å½•ï¼Œå¹¶å°†è§£å‹å‡ºçš„æ–‡ä»¶å¤¹é‡å‘½åä¸º <code>fluid</code>ã€‚</p><p>ä¿®æ”¹ç›®å½•<code>blog/_config.yml</code>æ–‡ä»¶ä¸­çš„</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install --save hexo-theme-fluid<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Then create <code>_config.fluid.yml</code> in the blog directory and copy the content of <code>_config.yml</code> from the theme folder. For release installation, download the latest release, then extract it to <code>themes</code> directory and rename it to <code>fluid</code>.<br>3. Set theme. Edit <code>_config.yml</code> in the blog root directory as follows:</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">theme:</span> <span class="hljs-string">fluid</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># Specify theme</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">language:</span> <span class="hljs-string">zh-CN</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># Specify language, will affect the theme display language, modify as needed</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="4"><li>Create about page. The about page needs to be created manually. Run the following command in the blog directory:</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo new page about<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Then edit <code>/source/about/index.md</code> under the blog directory and add <code>layout</code> attribute. The modified example is as follows:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">---<br>title: This is a title<br><span class="hljs-section">layout: about</span><br><span class="hljs-section">---</span><br><br>You can write the content here, with the support of Markdown and HTML<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Note</strong>: <code>layout: about</code> must exist and cannot be modified as other values, otherwise avatar and other styles will not be shown.<br>5. Deploy to GitHub. Install <code>hexo-deployer-git</code> that allows you to deploy your site. Run the following command in the blog directory:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install hexo-deployer-git<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Then edit <code>_config.yml</code> in the blog root directory, from the <code>deploy</code> section, add your deployment target information:</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">deploy:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">repo:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;repository</span> <span class="hljs-string">url&gt;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">branch:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;branch</span> <span class="hljs-string">name&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>From now on, once you finish writing, you can publish your posts via command:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>I hope this helps you create your personal blog with hexo and fluid theme. ğŸ˜Š</p><!-- ![å›¾ç‰‡å¼•ç”¨æ–¹æ³•ä¸‰](/images/test3.png) -->]]></content>
    
    
    
